questions: What were my total sales TIMEFRAME_PARAMETER?
templates.query: SELECT CONCAT('The total sales in the ', B.TIMEFRAME_DESC ,' timeframe is $', LTRIM(TO_VARCHAR(SUM(OP.NET_SALES_DOLLARS_TY), '999,999,999,990')) ) FROM PC.OPPORTUNITY_LOCATOR OP JOIN PC.LKP_TIMEFRAME B ON OP.TIMEFRAME_ID = B.TIMEFRAME_ID WHERE B.TIMEFRAME_ID = TIMEFRAME_PARAMETER AND OP.USED_IN_METRICS = TRUE AND STORE_CONCEPT_ID = 1 GROUP BY B.TIMEFRAME_DESC;

questions: What were my total sales in DEPARTMENTGROUP_PARAMETER TIMEFRAME_PARAMETER?
templates.query: SELECT CONCAT('The total sales in the ', B.TIMEFRAME_DESC ,' timeframe for the ', A.SALES_DEPARTMENT_GROUP_DISPLAY_LABEL,' department is $', LTRIM(TO_VARCHAR(SUM(OP.NET_SALES_DOLLARS_TY), '999,999,999,990')) ) FROM PC.OPPORTUNITY_LOCATOR OP JOIN PC.LKP_SALES_DEPARTMENT_GROUP A ON OP.SALES_DEPARTMENT_GROUP_ID = A.SALES_DEPARTMENT_GROUP_ID JOIN PC.LKP_TIMEFRAME B ON OP.TIMEFRAME_ID = B.TIMEFRAME_ID WHERE A.SALES_DEPARTMENT_GROUP_ID = DEPARTMENTGROUP_PARAMETER AND B.TIMEFRAME_ID = TIMEFRAME_PARAMETER AND OP.USED_IN_METRICS = TRUE AND STORE_CONCEPT_ID = 1 GROUP BY A.SALES_DEPARTMENT_GROUP_DISPLAY_LABEL, B.TIMEFRAME_DESC;

questions: What were my total sales in DEPARTMENTGROUP2_PARAMETER TIMEFRAME_PARAMETER?
templates.query: SELECT CONCAT('The total sales in the ', B.TIMEFRAME_DESC ,' timeframe in the ', 'DESCRIPTION_DEPARTMENTGROUP2_PARAMETER',' departments is $', LTRIM(TO_VARCHAR(SUM(OP.NET_SALES_DOLLARS_TY), '999,999,999,990')) ) FROM PC.OPPORTUNITY_LOCATOR OP JOIN PC.LKP_SALES_DEPARTMENT_GROUP A ON A.SALES_DEPARTMENT_GROUP_ID IN (DEPARTMENTGROUP2_PARAMETER) AND A.SALES_DEPARTMENT_GROUP_ID <> -1 JOIN PC.LKP_TIMEFRAME B ON OP.TIMEFRAME_ID = B.TIMEFRAME_ID WHERE OP.SALES_DEPARTMENT_GROUP_ID IN (DEPARTMENTGROUP2_PARAMETER) AND OP.TIMEFRAME_ID = TIMEFRAME_PARAMETER AND OP.USED_IN_METRICS = TRUE AND STORE_CONCEPT_ID = 1 GROUP BY A.SALES_DEPARTMENT_GROUP_DISPLAY_LABEL, B.TIMEFRAME_DESC;

questions: What were my total sales excluding EXCLUDE_DEPARTMENTGROUP_PARAMETER TIMEFRAME_PARAMETER?
What were my total sales not including EXCLUDE_DEPARTMENTGROUP_PARAMETER TIMEFRAME_PARAMETER?
templates.query: SELECT CONCAT('The total sales in the ', B.TIMEFRAME_DESC ,' timeframe excluding the ', A.SALES_DEPARTMENT_GROUP_DISPLAY_LABEL,' department is $', LTRIM(TO_VARCHAR(SUM(OP.NET_SALES_DOLLARS_TY), '999,999,999,990')) ) FROM PC.OPPORTUNITY_LOCATOR OP JOIN PC.LKP_SALES_DEPARTMENT_GROUP A ON A.SALES_DEPARTMENT_GROUP_ID NOT IN (EXCLUDE_DEPARTMENTGROUP_PARAMETER) AND A.SALES_DEPARTMENT_GROUP_ID <> -1 JOIN PC.LKP_TIMEFRAME B ON OP.TIMEFRAME_ID = B.TIMEFRAME_ID WHERE OP.SALES_DEPARTMENT_GROUP_ID IN (EXCLUDE_DEPARTMENTGROUP_PARAMETER) AND OP.TIMEFRAME_ID = TIMEFRAME_PARAMETER AND OP.USED_IN_METRICS = TRUE AND STORE_CONCEPT_ID = 1 GROUP BY A.SALES_DEPARTMENT_GROUP_DISPLAY_LABEL, B.TIMEFRAME_DESC;

questions: What were my total sales in STORE_PARAMETER TIMEFRAME_PARAMETER?
templates.query: SELECT CONCAT('The total sales in the ', B.TIMEFRAME_DESC ,' timeframe for the ', A.STORE_LABEL,' store is $', LTRIM(TO_VARCHAR(SUM(OP.NET_SALES_DOLLARS_TY), '999,999,999,990')) ) FROM PC.OPPORTUNITY_LOCATOR OP JOIN PC.LKP_STORE A ON OP.STORE_ID = A.STORE_ID JOIN PC.LKP_TIMEFRAME B ON OP.TIMEFRAME_ID = B.TIMEFRAME_ID WHERE A.STORE_ID = STORE_PARAMETER AND B.TIMEFRAME_ID = TIMEFRAME_PARAMETER AND OP.USED_IN_METRICS = TRUE AND STORE_CONCEPT_ID = 1 GROUP BY A.STORE_LABEL, B.TIMEFRAME_DESC;

templates.desc: Total sales at store STORENUM_PARAMETER in TIMEFRAME_PARAMETER.
questions: What were my total sales at Store STORENUM_PARAMETER in TIMEFRAME_PARAMETER?
templates.query: SELECT CONCAT('The total sales in the ', B.TIMEFRAME_DESC ,' timeframe for store ', A.STORE_NUMBER,' is $', LTRIM(TO_VARCHAR(SUM(OP.NET_SALES_DOLLARS_TY), '999,999,999,990')) ) FROM PC.OPPORTUNITY_LOCATOR OP JOIN PC.LKP_STORE A ON OP.STORE_ID = A.STORE_ID JOIN PC.LKP_TIMEFRAME B ON OP.TIMEFRAME_ID = B.TIMEFRAME_ID WHERE A.STORE_NUMBER = STORENUM_PARAMETER AND B.TIMEFRAME_ID = TIMEFRAME_PARAMETER AND OP.USED_IN_METRICS = TRUE AND STORE_CONCEPT_ID = 1 GROUP BY A.STORE_NUMBER, B.TIMEFRAME_DESC;

questions: What were my total sales at stores STORENUM2_PARAMETER TIMEFRAME_PARAMETER?
templates.query: SELECT CONCAT('The total sales in the ', B.TIMEFRAME_DESC ,' timeframe at stores ', 'DESCRIPTION_STORENUM2_PARAMETER',' is $', LTRIM(TO_VARCHAR(SUM(OP.NET_SALES_DOLLARS_TY), '999,999,999,990')) ) FROM PC.OPPORTUNITY_LOCATOR OP JOIN PC.LKP_STORE A ON A.STORE_ID IN (STORENUM2_PARAMETER) AND A.STORE_ID <> -1 JOIN PC.LKP_TIMEFRAME B ON OP.TIMEFRAME_ID = B.TIMEFRAME_ID WHERE OP.STORE_ID IN (STORENUM2_PARAMETER) AND OP.TIMEFRAME_ID = TIMEFRAME_PARAMETER AND OP.USED_IN_METRICS = TRUE AND STORE_CONCEPT_ID = 1 GROUP BY A.STORE_NUMBER, B.TIMEFRAME_DESC;

questions: What is my top performing store TIMEFRAME_PARAMETER?
templates.query: SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT(A.STORE_LABEL, ' is the top performing store in the ', B.TIMEFRAME_DESC ,' timeframe with $', LTRIM(TO_VARCHAR(SUM(OP.NET_SALES_DOLLARS_TY), '999,999,999,990')), ' of sales.' ) FROM PC.OPPORTUNITY_LOCATOR OP JOIN PC.LKP_STORE A ON OP.STORE_ID = A.STORE_ID JOIN PC.LKP_TIMEFRAME B ON OP.TIMEFRAME_ID = B.TIMEFRAME_ID WHERE B.TIMEFRAME_ID = TIMEFRAME_PARAMETER AND OP.USED_IN_METRICS = TRUE AND STORE_CONCEPT_ID = 1 GROUP BY A.STORE_LABEL, B.TIMEFRAME_DESC ORDER BY SUM(OP.NET_SALES_DOLLARS_TY) DESC;

templates.desc: The top performing store in SALES_GEOGRAPHY_PARAMETER TIMEFRAME_PARAMETER.
questions: What is the top performing store in SALES_GEOGRAPHY_PARAMETER TIMEFRAME_PARAMETER?
templates.query: SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT(A.STORE_LABEL, ' is the top performing store in ', C.SALES_GEOGRAPHY_DISPLAY_LABEL ,' in the ', B.TIMEFRAME_DESC,' timeframe with $', LTRIM(TO_VARCHAR(SUM(OP.NET_SALES_DOLLARS_TY), '999,999,999,990')), ' of sales.' ) FROM PC.OPPORTUNITY_LOCATOR OP JOIN PC.LKP_STORE A ON OP.STORE_ID = A.STORE_ID JOIN PC.LKP_TIMEFRAME B ON OP.TIMEFRAME_ID = B.TIMEFRAME_ID JOIN PC.LKP_SALES_GEOGRAPHY C ON OP.SALES_GEOGRAPHY_ID = C.SALES_GEOGRAPHY_ID WHERE B.TIMEFRAME_ID = TIMEFRAME_PARAMETER AND C.SALES_GEOGRAPHY_ID = SALES_GEOGRAPHY_PARAMETER AND OP.USED_IN_METRICS = TRUE AND STORE_CONCEPT_ID = 1 GROUP BY A.STORE_LABEL, B.TIMEFRAME_DESC, C.SALES_GEOGRAPHY_DISPLAY_LABEL ORDER BY SUM(OP.NET_SALES_DOLLARS_TY) DESC;

templates.desc: The top performing store in SALES_GEOGRAPHY_PARAMETER in DEPARTMENTGROUP_PARAMETER TIMEFRAME_PARAMETER.
questions: What is the top performing store in SALES_GEOGRAPHY_PARAMETER in DEPARTMENTGROUP_PARAMETER TIMEFRAME_PARAMETER?
templates.query: SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT(A.STORE_LABEL, ' is the top performing store in ', C.SALES_GEOGRAPHY_DISPLAY_LABEL , ' in ', D.SALES_DEPARTMENT_GROUP_DISPLAY_LABEL, ' in the ', B.TIMEFRAME_DESC,' timeframe with $', LTRIM(TO_VARCHAR(SUM(OP.NET_SALES_DOLLARS_TY), '999,999,999,990')), ' of sales.' ) FROM PC.OPPORTUNITY_LOCATOR OP JOIN PC.LKP_STORE A ON OP.STORE_ID = A.STORE_ID JOIN PC.LKP_TIMEFRAME B ON OP.TIMEFRAME_ID = B.TIMEFRAME_ID JOIN PC.LKP_SALES_GEOGRAPHY C ON OP.SALES_GEOGRAPHY_ID = C.SALES_GEOGRAPHY_ID JOIN PC.LKP_SALES_DEPARTMENT_GROUP D ON OP.SALES_DEPARTMENT_GROUP_ID = D.SALES_DEPARTMENT_GROUP_ID WHERE B.TIMEFRAME_ID = TIMEFRAME_PARAMETER AND C.SALES_GEOGRAPHY_ID = SALES_GEOGRAPHY_PARAMETER AND D.SALES_DEPARTMENT_GROUP_ID = DEPARTMENTGROUP_PARAMETER AND OP.USED_IN_METRICS = TRUE AND STORE_CONCEPT_ID = 1 GROUP BY A.STORE_LABEL, B.TIMEFRAME_DESC,C.SALES_GEOGRAPHY_DISPLAY_LABEL, D.SALES_DEPARTMENT_GROUP_DISPLAY_LABEL ORDER BY SUM(OP.NET_SALES_DOLLARS_TY) DESC;
